;-------Spider webbing for spidersilk clothes-------
INUMBER 1085
NAME 1085
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
ARTICLE some
IFPREVERB EXAM -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see a carefully wound ovoid of spiderwebbing.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB ROLL -1
 CLEARVERB
 IFNOITEM 8
  IFVAR SKILL15 > 34
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You carefully unwind the web, cleaning the glimmering strands of spidersilk.%c[Round: 15 sec]
    ECHO OTHERS %n carefully unwinds some spider webbing and cleans the glimmering strands of spidersilk.
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
    REMOVEITEM -1
    NEWITEM 8 585
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You clumsily try to unwind the web, and it becomes a tangled sticky mess in your fingers.%c[Round: 15 sec]
    REMOVEITEM -1
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
    APPEAR %n's hands are covered in gummy spiderwebbing.
    ECHO OTHERS %n clumsily picks at some spiderwebbing till it dissolves.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER There isn't enough room here to do this. Perhaps you should find another place.
 ENDIF 
ENDIF
;------------------------------
NOUNDEF 670 spidersilk
INUMBER 585
NAME 670
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
ARTICLE some
MATERIAL
SUBSTANCE CLOTH
dyeable
PARAMETER1 437
PARAMETER2 15
IFPREVERB WORK -1
  IFVAR SKILL15 < 41
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You try to work the spidersilk, but it dissolves into a tangled mess.
    REMOVEITEM -1
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ENDIF
ENDIF
