*description_start
From the venom-dripping mandibles, to the eight slender legs effortlessly skittering across tangled webbing, this gigantic spider inspires only awe and terror. The feelings are heightened by the red hourglass shape which is visible upon the spider's abdomen.
*description_end
texe A dark shape skitters in along the webbing.
texg A dark shape drops abruptly from above.
texd falls over to lay on her back, legs curled.
texm A dark widow moves along webs to the
texa A dark widow drops towards
texs A dark widow's abdomen undulates with a disturbing ripple of motion.
texl A dark widow whips its abdomen forward
texq A gout of sticky substance flies out, yet misses its target.
tex1 A large shape leaps past overhead.
tex2 A dark widow hunkers down for a moment, as if preparing to leap.
texh A dark widow fails to slip into a shadow.
texv Something moves in the shadows.
