*DESCRIPTION_START
You see an acolyte of one of the local temples, his features concealed in an all-encompassing dark hooded garment. His attitude is one of quiet reflection.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MANA 200
SPELLUSE 25
SPELLSKILL 120
CASTLEVEL 70
SPELL 105
SPELL 314
SPELL 312
TEXE An acolyte quietly enters the area.
TEXQ Magical energies sputter about an acolyte's hands.
TEXZ An acolyte contemplates the dead form of %s.
TEXD falls to the ground without a sound.
TEXM An acolyte steps quietly
TEXG An acolyte rises from a place of meditation in the shadows.
TEXS An acolyte breaks his silence to incant a spell.
TEXL An acolyte gestures
TEXA An acolyte bows and steps towards
TEXR An acolyte steps back.
TEX1 A hooded acolyte nods to you enigmatically.
TEX2 A hooded acolyte pauses in silent contemplation.
TEX3 A hooded acolyte makes an intricate gesture of malediction with his long-fingered hands.
