SCRIPTMACRO 89
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a face ravaged by a lifetime of submission to those with power over him. He is clothed in simple grey sackcloth which exposes malnourished limbs to the harsh atmosphere in this realm.
*DESCRIPTION_END
TEXE A slave shuffles in.
TEXZ A slave gazes at %s, a strange gleeful light filling his eyes.
TEX1 A slave shuffles out of your path.
TEX2 A slave casts his eyes to the ground in your presence.
TEX3 A slave mutters a rote apology for his unworthy presence.
TEXD barely has time to fall to the ground, before being seized and hauled away.
TEXF A slave scrambles
TEXM A slave shuffles
TEXG A slave shuffles in.
TEXR A slave backs away in terror.
