NUMBER 52
NAME Web-Filled Caves
DEEPCAVE
REGION 5
MINEA
CHANNEL 147
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls sparkle strangely in the dim light as you find yourself in a larger cavern. The everpresent webbing drapes down from the hidden ceiling like some horrendous noble's dressing chamber. An oddly shaped altar rests against the east wall of the cave.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NE 53
EXIT E 51
ITEM 1 420 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=944
ITEM 2 1396 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=687
ITEM 3 236 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=218 VAL2=20
EXTEND 3 in the shape of a large round-bodied spider
ITEM 4 324 ADJ1=442 ADJ2=87
EXTEND 4 in the back of the spider shaped altar
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
This waist-high altar is carved from a solid block of jet black obsidian. It takes the shape of a giant, round-bodied spider with a pool of some dark liquid in the center of its back.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
This small pool of liquid is only a few inches deep, but extends for many feet down the length of the long spider-shaped altar. It is filled with some dark, caustic liquid, as evidenced by the noxious vapors and constant bubbling from its surface.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The rough cavern wall glistens with a black viscous liquid that which forms a thin coating over its entire surface. The liquid seemingly seeps forth from deep within the rock itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The webbing is enormous, filling the gap between ceiling and floor with ease. It falls in sweeping lengths all about you in the darkness.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 18
IFENTRY
 IFVAR DISGUISED = 1
  ECHO ALL A strange rune, etched in the ceiling, glows.
  SPELL 250 99
 ENDIF
 IFVAR WIELDED ! 0
  IFCARRY WIELDED -1
   IFVAR ITEMADJ1 = 752
    IFVAR ITEMADJ2 = 684
     ECHO PLAYER As you walk along, your weapon slices through the thick webbing with ease.
    ELSE
     EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
     ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
    ENDIF
   ELSE
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
    ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
   ENDIF
  ELSE
   EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
   ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL 2
 CLEARVERB
 ADD ROUNDTIME 15
 ADD ITEMVAL5 1
 ECHO PLAYER You attempt to pull some of the webbing free from the tangled webs.
 ECHO OTHERS %n attempts to pull some of the webbing free from the tangled webs.
 EQUAL DUMMY3 skill18
 SUB DUMMY3 ITEMVAL5
 RANDOM DUMMY4 1 100 0
 IFVAR DUMMY4 <= DUMMY3
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You successfully pull a wad of webbing free.
  ECHO OTHERS %n successfully pulls a wad of webbing free.
  NEWITEM -1 1085 ADJ2=545
 ELSE
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You only succeed in further tangling the webbing.
  ECHO OTHERS %n only succeeds in further tangling the webbing.
  RANDOM DUMMY3 1 3 0
  IFVAR DUMMY3 ! 2
   spell 127 99
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT 4
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You place %a into the pool in the center of the altar.
 ECHO OTHERS %n places %a into the pool in the center of the altar.
 EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
 ECHO ALL The liquid hisses and bubbles around %a as it is lowered beneath the surface.
 IFVAR ITEMADJ1 = 684
  IFVAR SKILL8 > 5
   SETITEMADJ -1 1 752
   SETITEMADJ -1 2 684
   SETITEMVAL -1 3 23
   SETITEMVAL -1 5 2
   SETITEMADJ -1 3 -1
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO ALL The item in the pool begins to take on an iridescent hue as the liquid burns away all evidence of the original substance.
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER Your expertise in weaponsmithing allows you to realize the proper timing, and you confidently remove the item from the pool.
   ECHO OTHERS %n deftly snatches the now iridescent item from the pool.
  ELSE
   REMOVEITEM -1
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO ALL The item in the pool begins to take on an iridescent hue.
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER You begin to realize that something might be wrong.
   PLREVENT 0
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO ALL The item in the pool seemingly dissolves after being left too long in the liquid.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  REMOVEITEM -1
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The item in the pool is completely dissolved by the corrosive liquid.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
 ECHO PLAYER You hear strange chittering noise from the shadows of the cavern, and for a moment, are certain something large made a sound above you.
ENDIF
IFVERB TOUCH 1
 ECHO PLAYER The wall is slick and oily to the touch.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 2
 CLEARVERB
 EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
 ECHO PLAYER You reach out and pull at the webbing.
 ECHO OTHERS %n reaches out and pulls at the webbing.
 spell 127 99
ENDIF
