ITEM 1 420 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=944
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The rough cavern wall glistens with a black viscous liquid that which forms a thin coating over its entire surface. The liquid seemingly seeps forth from deep within the rock itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;------------------------------
ITEM 2 1396 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=687
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The webbing is enormous, filling the gap between ceiling and floor with ease. You wonder at the size of the creature that created it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;-----------ucantsee-----------
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
;------------------------------
MONSTER_GROUP 18
IFENTRY
 IFVAR DISGUISED = 1
  ECHO ALL A strange rune, etched in the ceiling, glows.
  SPELL 250 99
 ENDIF
 IFVAR WIELDED ! 0
  IFCARRY WIELDED -1
   IFVAR ITEMADJ1 = 752
    IFVAR ITEMADJ2 = 684
     ECHO PLAYER As you walk along, your weapon slices through the thick webbing with ease.
    ELSE
     EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
     ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
    ENDIF
   ELSE
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
    ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
   ENDIF
  ELSE
   EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
   ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ECHO PLAYER The thick webbing catches at you and slows you down.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL 2
 CLEARVERB
 ADD ROUNDTIME 15
 ADD ITEMVAL5 1
 ECHO PLAYER You attempt to pull some of the webbing free from the tangled webs.
 ECHO OTHERS %n attempts to pull some of the webbing free from the tangled webs.
 EQUAL DUMMY3 skill18
 SUB DUMMY3 ITEMVAL5
 RANDOM DUMMY4 1 100 0
 IFVAR DUMMY4 <= DUMMY3
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You successfully pull a wad of webbing free.
  ECHO OTHERS %n successfully pulls a wad of webbing free.
  NEWITEM -1 1085 ADJ2=545
 ELSE
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER You only succeed in further tangling the webbing.
  ECHO OTHERS %n only succeeds in further tangling the webbing.
  RANDOM DUMMY3 1 3 0
  IFVAR DUMMY3 ! 2
   spell 127 99
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
 ECHO PLAYER You hear faint scratching and chittering noises from the shadows all about you.
 PLREVENT 4
 CONTPLREVENT
 RANDOM DUMMY3 1 7 0
 IFVAR DUMMY3 = 4
  ECHO PLAYER From somewhere in the shadows ahead you hear a sibillant voice, "What hass it gots in its pocketsess, my preciouss?"
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB TOUCH 1
 ECHO PLAYER The wall is slick and oily to the touch.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 2
 CLEARVERB
 EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
 ECHO PLAYER You reach out and pull at the webbing.
 ECHO OTHERS %n reaches out and pulls at the webbing.
 spell 127 99
ENDIF
