wrathful, multilimbed, female deity sensuously wreathed in sulphurous clouds of
fire and smoke. Two crimson eyes like molten rubies glare down into the room
from a skull-like face. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
;-----------ucantsee-----------
ITEM 9 693 ADJ1=50
CALL 33
