NUMBER 67
NAME Avenue of the Gods
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
REGION 5
CHANNEL 147
MONSTER_GROUP 20
*DESCRIPTION_START
The left side of this blood-red avenue is bounded by the local slave pens. Vast numbers of shackled slaves, prisoners and terrified animals await their turn at the auction block. The auctioneer and his brawny assistants manfully  drag creature after creature to the auction block, where they're sold off in an efficient and ruthless manner. The avenue continues north and south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 57
EXIT S 68
;-----------ucantsee-----------
ITEM 9 693 ADJ1=50
CALL 33
;------------------------------
IFVERB GAZE -1
  PLREVENT 0
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER Your gaze is drawn to the impossible buildings...
  PLREVENT 0
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER Your eyes try to take in the massive shape rising to the north, but your mind seems to be unable to grasp it fully. What you can understand is this is a four stepped pyramid build of some strange green material. Stairs rise up its sides.
  ECHO PLAYER You look at the building far to the south and your mind plays tricks with you. It seems very near, or how else could it be so large. It is black and its towers rise impossibly high.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
 PLREVENT 0
 CONTPLREVENT
 ECHO PLAYER You hear the quiet moans of the shackled slaves.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PAY -1
 CLEARVERB
 EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
 ECHO PLAYER You catch the auctioneer's attention.
 ECHO OTHERS %n catches the auctioneer's attention.
 PLREVENT 0
 CONTPLREVENT
 IFVAR ILZARAUCTION ! 0
  EQUAL RITUALVAL2 ILZARAUCTION
  IFVAR WEALTH5 >= ILZARPRICE
   EQUAL ILZARAUCTION 0
   SUB WEALTH5 ILZARPRICE
   STRCVT 0 ILZARPRICE
   ECHO PLAYER You hand %0 darktars to the auctioneer.
   ECHO OTHERS %n hands %0 darktars to the auctioneer.
   EQUAL ILZARPRICE 0
   PLREVENT 0
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER The auctioneer makes a ritual gesture, binding you to your purchase.
   ECHO OTHERS The auctioneer makes a ritual gesture, binding %n to %h purchase.
   SPELL 2 99
   PLREVENT 0
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER Your new purchase steps forward to your side.
   ECHO OTHERS %n's new purchase steps forward to %h side.
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER The auctioneer sneers at you for attempting to buy without sufficient darktars.
   ECHO OTHERS The auctioneer sneers at %n for attempting to buy without sufficient darktars.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO ALL The auctioneer says, "Sorry, this lot has already been sold."
 ENDIF
ENDIF
