*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand on the north end of an unusual island. It seems perfectly round and the ground beneath your feet is formed of what appears to be a single piece of the strange black material. It is so dark it seems to drink all the light in the area. To the south your eyes are drawn to an awesome sight. There stands a towering cathedral made of the same substance. Its towers and spires soar into the sky until the tops disappear into the clouds. The architecture is unworldly unlike anything ever seem on Andor before. Massive steps lead up to a carved black door placed just below a huge stained glass window in the shape of a vast red eye. To the north is a bridge.
*DESCRIPTION_END
