NUMBER 73
NAME Dark Cathedral, The Center
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 149
FIXED_LIGHT
REGION 5
*DESCRIPTION_START
The piers of The Center soar ninety-eight feet to the vaulting. Inset in the
marble floor is the Eye of Dahkahn, the Cathedral's special symbol. Located at
the southeast corner of The Center, the Grand Pulpit stands ten feet tall on
its stone pillars. The stones for the Pulpit look to be some unusually dense
crystal that seems to shift and move internally. The Pulpit is covered with
carvings that depict the history of Dahkahn. A flight of stairs lead up into
the Grand Pulpit. Through an immense arch the High Altar gleams. A door leads
deeper into the cathedral.
*DESCRIPTION_END
