NUMBER 74
NAME Dark Cathedral, Library
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
REGION 5
*DESCRIPTION_START
Dahkahn while known as The Devourer of Souls, is also known by his followers as
a devourer of knowledge. Here is the beginning of a great library for his loyal
minons. Rows of shelves have been installed in this vast room. At present most
of the shelves are empty but a number of black robed scribes are busy with the
task of logging each and every book and scroll into the huge catalog at one end
of the room and then placing them on the shelves.  
*DESCRIPTION_END
;------------ door out of the Library------------
ITEM 0 65 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=169 VAL2=73 UNLOCKED OPEN
;------------ catalog ------------
ITEM 1 267 ADJ1=163
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
This is a huge book that catalogs the name, author and location of all the books and scrolls in the library.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB OPEN 1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 145
	ECHO PLAYER The catalog seems to be magically sealed.
	ECHO OTHERS Something stops %n from touching the book.
  ELSE
	IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER You have already opened the catalog.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
		ECHO PLAYER Black fire opens the seal of the catalog.
		ECHO OTHERS As %n reaches for the catalog a black glow moves from %h fingers to the catalog, causing it to open.		
		EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
	ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CLOSE 1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 145
	ECHO PLAYER The catalog seems to be magically protected.
	ECHO OTHERS Something stops %n from touching the catalog.
  ELSE
	IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
		ECHO PLAYER You have already closed the catalog.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Black fire seals the catalog.
		ECHO OTHERS As %n reaches for the catalog a black glow moves from %h fingers to the catalog, causing it to close.		
		EQUAL ITEMVAL1 0
	ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB READ 1
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
	ECHO PLAYER The catalog is closed.
 ENDIF
 IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 1
	ECHO PLAYER Shelf B7-12  "The History of The Dread Lord Vol 1"  Anonymous
	ECHO PLAYER Shelf B7-13  "The History of The Dread Lord Vol 4"  Anonymous
	ECHO PLAYER Shelf B7-14  "The History of The Dread Lord Vol 7"  Anonymous
	ECHO PLAYER Shelf B7-16  "Alchemy, the Hidden Art"  Tecihemenos 
 ENDIF
ENDIF
