    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL The Great Choir finishes the hymn and the Organ goes quiet.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL The Eye of Dahkahn opens and His Dread Gaze falls upon the assembled worshippers.
ENDIF
