NAME Ilzar, Market Square
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 147
REGION 5
MONSTER_GROUP 20
*DESCRIPTION_START
Tendrils of fog curl caressingly around the statue that juts from the center of a new fountain in this cobble-stoned square. The fog extends outwards in all directions, draping the surrounding buildings in a hazy curtain of dim gray hue. Openings lead into several newly built market stalls around you, and the voices from them seem to suggest that the New Ilzar is far more posperous than the old.
*DESCRIPTION_END
