REGION 5
*DESCRIPTION_START
The bailey of the Dark Keep is a huge common room, it has long tables running down each wall, with ample benches to sit upon. At the northern end of the room is the High Table where the leaders sit. Behind the table is an archway leading deeper into the Keep. The walls are covered in rich dark tapestries that both decorate and keep the room warm.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;------------------------ door out -------------
ITEM 0 943 ADJ1=355 VAL1=999 VAL2=85 VAL3=66 UNLOCKED
;-------------------archway into inner sanctum -----------
ITEM 1 60 ADJ1=25
IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ORG = 23
    ECHO PLAYER You pass through the arch as the shadows bow to you.
    ECHO OTHERS %P passes through the black arch.
    MOVEGROUP 87
    AFFECT 87
    ECHO OTHERS %P appears slowly in front of you.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The shadows of the arch push you away.
    ECHO OTHERS Shadows push %P back from the black arch.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;-----------ucantsee-----------
ITEM 9 693 ADJ1=50
CALL 33
;------------------------------
NUMBER 87
NAME Dark Guard Keep, Inner Sanctum
ASTRAL
CHANNEL 147
REGION 5
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Polished black marble walls, floor and ceiling, striated with flecks of silver form the interior of this stunning chamber. Carefully engraved across the surface of the slightly upward curving walls are sterling silver versions of a vast number of weapons. Engraved scenes of armor clad warriors defending priests and mages in shadowy cloaks of black round out the startling imagery. Placed in the center of the chamber is a black obsidian altar with some writing upon it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;------------------------------
ITEM 0 236 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=218
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Engraved in bold silver lettering upon the altar are the words, "To Defend, To Guard, To Uphold our Ideals, To Strive for the Power that is ours! The pledge of the Dark Guard is eternally binding, do not fail us."
*DESCRIPTION_END
;-----------ucantsee-----------
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
;------------------------------
EXIT O 86
ORGDEF 23 INVITE GUILD 87 Dark_Guard
TRAINING 1 88
TRAINING 2 40
TRAINING 6 104
TRAINING 7 31
TRAINING 10 45
TRAINING 12 30
